\n< Serena >...There are four thugs. Almost
unarmed. For thugs, they're quite
well-dressed...

\n< Serena >...They're wandering around without any
tension. Are they unaware that they're
dealing with contraband?

\n< Serena >Enough observation. It's about time to
start cleaning up.
\n< Man >Whoa!? Who's there?!

\n< Serena >Even if I told you my name, you lot
wouldn't understand, would you?

\n< Serena >Well... let's just say I'm an adventurer
from the city. The purpose of my visit
should be obvious, right?

\n< Man >Tch, putting on airs! You're really
getting on my nerves!

\n< Man >You think a brat like you can take us on
alone? You've got guts! We'll wrap you
up and toss you in the river!

\n< Serena >I struggled a bit... I still have much
to learn.
\n< Serena >They were hardly a challenge.

\n< Serena >They're not from the hot spring town.
But they don't seem like they've been
camping or traveling for long either.

\n< Serena >Perhaps they're from that town to the
east. Yes, that would make sense.

The bridge should be impassable, so
maybe they crossed the river by boat.
But where could the boat be... No, the
risk is too great.\n< Serena >

Anyway, the request has been resolved.
Whether it's poison or a boat, I'll
leave the rest to the Guild Master.\n< Serena >

The town to the east... must be quite a
rough place. Splendor...\n< Serena >

Understood. I'll take care of the rest.
Good work out there.\n< Guild Master >
Do these types show up often?\n< Serena >

Not all the time, but this isn't the
first time either.\n< Guild Master >

Prohibition and restrictions,
ironically, create a strong demand.\n< Guild Master >

There are many forests and woods by the
river. In the cover of night, even
patrol eyes...\n< Guild Master >

...Hey, you're not thinking of doing
something bad, are you?\n< Guild Master >

To say I hadn't considered it would be a
lie. But to take that approach now would
be a detour.\n< Serena >

If only I had thought of this method on
my first day in this town...\n< Serena >
Hey now...\n< Guild Master >

Well, it's good that we have a backup
plan.\n< Serena >

If you don't want criminals coming out
of the guild, then you'd better keep
sending me work promptly.\n< Serena >
Yes yes, as you wish.\n< Guild Master >
\V[2501]\n< Serena > left... One more thing.
'クエストをクリアした。'
'　人間相手に戦うのは初めての事であった。少し疲れた気がする。宿に帰ろう。'
